channel.title: Would someone please help me make a server >?
channel.description: hey guys ive been trying to make a server for a day no luck :@ i was wondering if someone would be kind enough to help me make one so i can get it up and running please someone help

item.title: Would someone please help me make a server >?
item.dc:creator: @Adecker246 Adecker246
item.description:
@Adecker246 wrote:

[quote=“Sanskrit, post:18, topic:371807”][quote author=Adecker246 link=topic=467875.msg3420761#msg3420761 date=1291495920]
public class youFail{
public static void main(String[] args){
System.out.println(“This is java…In its most simplest form”);
}
}

That is java. Its code. Its computer language. Google “Java basics” and read. Learn. Good luck.

EDIT: Just incase you don’t understand. Java is what RS is written in. You must change and code Java to make a new server.
[/quote]

Actually Runescape content is written in a language created by Jagex called “RuneScript”, but the engine is still purely Java. You can read about it here: http://runescape.wikia.com/wiki/RuneScript[/quote]
Really? That is something I never knew. I knew they had they own API’s and stuff (private of course) but didn’t know they named it. Thats cool Well thanks for the info but you still need to know Java to make a server.
